<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Attendance Marked</title>
    <style>
        /* Add your custom styles here */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 100px;
            height: auto;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/c01682bb-8bb5-45bd-b1eb-3cb2483fae49/blob-a5edcdc.png/:/rs=w:104,h:104,cg:true,m/cr=w:104,h:104/qt=q:95" alt="<%= org %> Logo" class="logo">
            <h1>Attendance Marked</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= volunteer.email %>,</p>
            <p>Your attendance for <%= xsession.name %> - <%= xsession.date.toDateString() %> has been successfully marked on <%= attendance.updatedAt.toLocaleString() %>.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding your attendance, please don't hesitate to reach out to us.</p>
            <p>Thank you for your cooperation!</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br><%= org %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent to <%= volunteer.email %></p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 <%= org %>. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
